textBeforeTable: The Battlefield 1942 Website now features a new trailer from Battlefield Vietnam, offering the chance to check out more of the gameplay in the upcoming Vietnam War shooter. The 1:42 clip shows off some jungle warfare in and over the Mekong Delta. ActiveX is required to view the streaming clip, so non-IE browsers may have trouble with this.
